query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi.info in ('Tatar','Icelandic','None','Serbian','Welsh','Polish','Chinese','Urdu','Ukrainian','Mandarin','Kyrgyz') AND k.keyword not like '%secrets%' AND k.keyword not like '%escape%' AND k.keyword not like '%fantasy%' AND (n.name like '%K%' OR n.name like '%t%') AND mi_idx.info > '2.0' AND it1.info in ('admissions','LD digital sound','printed media reviews','LD official retail price','LD language','votes','LD master format','LD video quality','LD audio quality','LD additional information','locations','screenplay-teleplay','rentals','LD dynamic range','LD sharpness','quotes','trivia','LD disc size','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','LD number of sides','LD year')
